{"tid":790671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反 唔講咁多 即刻駁嘴","createTime":"2018-08-23T07:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T12:22:00.000Z","uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"239037c433a9d3925993537d1fa9a6db53f260ae","tid":790671,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:57:20.000Z","msg":"呢度係專針對人地叫你做乜做<br />\n你唔做仲懶係串馬人嘴嗰啲煩西<br />\n<br />\n所以我決定用以其人之道還其人之身<br />\n用駁嘴駁返佢地嘴令佢地冇野好講<br />\n<br />\n例如 <br />\n：屌啲野好撚難食<br />\n：你都唔識食就返去食一丁啦<br />\n：<span style=\"color: red;\">咁唔通要做廚師先可以批評<br />\n要跑得快過隻馬先可以講馬？</span><br />\n：<span style=\"color: teal;\">咁你係咪食家？有冇講馬佬咁口齒 伶俐 獻醜不如藏拙啦</span><br />\n：er....<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇一啲好例子 或者駁法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔講咁多 即刻駁嘴</span>"},{"pid":"2120a65d5965cb18456f5a0e5eb0b8a4b1fda440","tid":790671,"uid":15,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:59:24.000Z","msg":"條條大路通羅馬"},{"pid":"99f0ec0a88d59fca8b34b3a9d9d0a343f0f47e9b","tid":790671,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2120a65d5965cb18456f5a0e5eb0b8a4b1fda440","tid":790671,"uid":15,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T07:59:24.000Z","msg":"條條大路通羅馬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"條條陰間通大路"},{"pid":"72f8d4e704619480911e0394f00ce04db090bed2","tid":790671,"uid":140573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:32:27.000Z","msg":"樓豬<br />\n抄襲當自創"},{"pid":"c4476ea9ba672ac54abde470e5d756f16d5d9357","tid":790671,"uid":191974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T09:34:29.000Z","msg":"行行出狀元<br />\n<br />\n馬中出赤兔"},{"pid":"7cd97a2cf3f69124cc52c990a55b3c117a5650f7","tid":790671,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T10:02:20.000Z","msg":"臭你又奶？"},{"pid":"40fb7b1d094c3b41be879f5c2b701aa308c4c384","tid":790671,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc